      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable car without the 'new car' price tag! I've taken great care of it, and it's totally ready to hit the road with a new owner today. You're going to love how it handles, so come take it for a spin!",
